plot: A cyclist's homicide introduces Nick (David Giuntoli) and Hank (Russell Hornsby) to a Wesen with a tragic fatal touch. Captain Renard (Sasha Roiz) and Adalind (Claire Coffee) learn the Royals have stepped up their efforts to find their child, and another member of the Royal family (guest star Nico Evers-Swindell) is introduced. Meanwhile, Juliette (Bitsie Tulloch) ponders the idea of embracing what she's become as opposed to fighting it.

Nick's team tracks down the poisonous feral frog who killed -without intent- people witnessing involuntary transformations, notably in their cycling club. As if Renard's bleeding nightmares weren't bad enough, vindictive Juliette extends her threat even to him, demanding help to eliminate Adalind. Prince Kenneth, now in charge of recuperating the royal baby, however keeps his pregnant Hexenbiest under close enough watch.—KGF Vissers
